title: When will SpaceX's Falcon 9 rocket return to flight after 4 upper-stage issues in 19 months?
description: For the fourth time in the last 19 months, the upper stage of SpaceX's Falcon 9 rocket experienced a problem during a mission. How long will the vehicle be grounded this time?
